Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.88,0:02:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,1,867... 1,868...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.89,0:02:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,1,869...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.45,0:02:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I got one!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.49,0:02:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.55,0:02:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.83,0:02:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! I've got something, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.46,0:02:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is big! \NThis could be the guardian fish for this area!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.72,0:02:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.56,0:02:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.99,0:03:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Guardian fish...?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.99,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't eat that at all...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.66,0:03:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't even caught a single fish yet! \NDon't complain!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then. Just watch.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.91,0:03:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna catch a big one!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.96,0:03:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you catch any?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I will somehow...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.83,0:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.84,0:03:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you a tropical juice \Nthat's great for your beauty
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and makes your skin smooth!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.61,0:03:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I want some, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.16,0:03:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Smooth skin!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.49,0:03:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.90,0:03:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you want smooth skin for?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To get cuter!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind's fine. The current is fine, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we won't have any problems today.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's taken the bait!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.42,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.09,0:04:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.68,0:04:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy! What'd you catch?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What a huge turban shell!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.69,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's not actually a turban shell.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What're we gonna do with it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if this is edible...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna eat it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe cook it in its shell?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you too?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.21,0:04:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... Boy, I thought I'd die!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.97,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who... are you...?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.93,0:04:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Pardon me for not \Nintroducing myself sooner.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.98,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,With a single call, I'll cordially \Ndeliver products to your town.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.36,0:05:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Rice Rice from Transponder Snail Mail-Order.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Very nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.03,0:05:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Transponder Snail Mail-Order? What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.99,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was in the process of \Nmaking a delivery with the Escar,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but I got caught in a heavy storm
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.12,0:05:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and got shipwrecked with the \Nwaves throwing me to and fro.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,– I see... \N– You must've been shaken up.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.42,0:05:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaken and stirred.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.93,0:05:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. You're quite clever, Miss!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, drink some water.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.14,0:05:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't much, but as a token of my gratitude,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you these catalogues.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With a single call, I'll deliver the products to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's convenient.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll deliver even when we're on the sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That, I can't.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.28,0:05:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... really...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.74,0:05:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.70,0:05:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our motto is safe, reliable and cheap.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,– And our mission is... \N– It's quite roomy inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Our company is, believe it or not...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.58,0:06:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,– Ahh! What're you guys doing?! \N– Wh-What's this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.17,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! \NThis is what I'm going to introduce to you today.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.71,0:06:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buru Buru Blade, \Nwhich is familiar to people by now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.89,0:06:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buru Buru Blade is our company's top product.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.35,0:06:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And today, I'll introduce you to this new model!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.23,0:06:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that many of you are already \Nusing the old Buru Buru Blade.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.03,0:06:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But the old model didn't, well, \Nlet you change the weight load,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.36,0:06:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,which was bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.74,0:06:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fine for fathers,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.62,0:06:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but many wanted small \Nchildren to be able to use it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't know what it is, but it looks fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.12,0:06:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this new model lets you \Nkeep a certain rhythm and...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.58,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.67,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know all about this one, right?! \NThis is the Abu Abu Slider.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Our company's No. 1 product!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.93,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A new model has been released! \NGive this a try!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.80,0:06:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How is "top" different from "No. 1"?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.76,0:06:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.77,0:06:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And, this is our best-selling product! \NThe "Golden Fish"!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.64,0:07:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is recommended for people \Nwho don't exercise much these days.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.94,0:07:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll offer these great weight loss \Nproducts together as a set!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And, today only, I'll also add
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.61,0:07:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,20 bottles of plenty sweet Mero Mero Juice made in the West Blue,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.07,0:07:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,a 26-volume encyclopedia set \Nthat will definitely be useful,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.67,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and a pair of binoculars that are \Nconvenient for various things!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How much do you think all this would cost?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A pretty penny, to be sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.04,0:07:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Today only, I present this as a token \Nof my gratitude for saving my life!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna give them to us?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take them, you thieves!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.38,0:07:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How about 23,800 Berries?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're selling them...!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.39,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I want them!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna buy them?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.77,0:07:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You carry kitchen knives, too?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! You're talking about this, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.82,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one of the high-quality items \Nproduced individually and carefully
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,by a craftsman in High Mountain.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this elasticity.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.20,0:07:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And its excellent sharpness will last forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A dozen table knives,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,a pair of all-purpose kitchen \Nscissors that can cut anything,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.54,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a paring knife, and an electric whetstone! \NI'll add all these!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you act now, it's 2,980 Berries!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.67,0:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, Miss, here is a Smooth Skin Soap!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.17,0:08:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It can make your skin as smooth as an egg!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... You do have everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.56,0:08:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.43,0:08:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,From mineral water to cannonballs, \Nthere's nothing we don't carry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You have living things, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we don't.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You don't?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have what we don't carry, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, do you have paper?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Paper?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. \NStrong paper that's big and hard to tear,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.87,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,so that it'll take more than a \Nsmall sea breeze to get damaged.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.70,0:08:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, please leave it to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.33,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Transponder Snail Mail-Order \Npresents with confidence
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.83,0:08:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the best paper, A-Thousand-Year Paper!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Thousand-Year Paper?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.80,0:08:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Thousand-Year Paper is manufactured \Nby using the A-Thousand-Year Tree
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that naturally grows on Eight-Nine Island.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This paper keeps away bugs, \Nand it's said that it won't fade
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.76,0:09:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,for at least a thousand years, \Neven if it's kept exposed to the sun.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.31,0:09:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best for writing family \Ntrees or drawing treasure maps.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Paper airplanes, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.94,0:09:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be a waste...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So how much is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna buy it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.32,0:09:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I caught her purchasing desire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.66,0:09:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I take it she's the type that price is \Nno object once she decides to buy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.37,0:09:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, I'll just stir up her urge to buy as \Nmuch as possible and jack up the price.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're interested...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.71,0:09:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a valuable item in short supply...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you order now,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.71,0:09:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it'll be available in five years... or ten...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.05,0:09:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't there some way you could sell it to me?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay any price.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.43,0:09:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.23,0:09:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nami who would rather count money than eat her meals...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.31,0:09:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nami who is a money monger...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...will pay any price?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.94,0:09:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys're going too far...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.78,0:10:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then... If you insist that much...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A ream of 1,000 A-Thousand-Year Papers
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,normally costs 60 million Berries,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.37,0:10:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but how about a special price of 48 million?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.55,0:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,48 million Berries...!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that it costs \N48,000 Berries a sheet?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you drop the price a little more?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.68,0:10:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll make it a lot cheaper...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.09,0:10:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How about 47.5 million Berries?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.93,0:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,2 million Berries!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,4.8 million Berries!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.72,0:10:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This sounds fishy...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.72,0:10:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you go cheaper?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.89,0:10:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll buy it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.69,0:10:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the money?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.65,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.98,0:10:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we hand him over to the Navy, \Nwe'll have that and change.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.74,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Luffy. This is for Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy...?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.57,0:10:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.54,0:10:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy... You mean... that Monkey D. Luffy?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji! Whatever, just untie me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.73,0:10:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.68,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Th-That odious pirate with \Na 100 million-Berry bounty...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.39,0:11:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That Monkey D. Luffy...?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.46,0:11:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it... that's a pirate flag!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.44,0:11:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I missed such important details!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.20,0:11:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I said untie me!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.62,0:11:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm...!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.94,0:11:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered that I have \Nan important appointment.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.32,0:11:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.87,0:11:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you forgot something...!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.54,0:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was scared of you...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanted man, Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.10,0:11:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. I'm going to work now, \Nso don't interrupt me, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "work"?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.98,0:11:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not cute, you know...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.19,0:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone near you \Nuntil you're done with the work.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.03,0:12:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what if the wind direction \Nsuddenly changes or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Those clouds...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If they don't move,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll have a fine day today \Nand there'll be no problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.21,0:12:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come get me only when something \Nchanges with those clouds.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have been hectic
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and I haven't had free time since \Nwe entered the Grand Line, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Garden...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Drum Island...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.90,0:12:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alabasta...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.48,0:12:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've written down all the routes that we took.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.78,0:12:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've stolen... no, obtained maps of the \Nsurrounding areas from towns as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.37,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll draw... my own world map...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,my dream since childhood...!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.43,0:13:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.35,0:13:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make the deck spick-and-span \Nwhile Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}'s working.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.73,0:13:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.24,0:13:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.77,0:13:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna do it, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.98,0:13:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,– You traitor! \N– No fair!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,– That's right! \N– Then what about that woman?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.77,0:13:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous! She's a lady!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.46,0:13:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How stupid! \NIt doesn't matter if it's a man or woman...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.37,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just help us, Mosshead monster!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.79,0:13:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha, very funny, Love-Love Machine goblin.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just help us, or I'll beat you up, you bastard.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.71,0:13:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. \NYou think you can beat the monster?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.34,0:13:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that because you \Ndon't know my goblin power.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.76,0:13:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.15,0:14:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut you down!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.25,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to gut you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut you into pieces!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.99,0:14:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.24,0:14:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it, both of you...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.91,0:14:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Don't just stand there and watch. \NLet's stop them already..
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.84,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous! \NDon't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know there's no way I can stop them.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you to be quiet?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.43,0:14:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mellorine...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just one hit...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.60,0:14:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For Pete's sake...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Bellemere-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellemere-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellemere-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.70,0:14:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.41,0:14:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, where does the wind come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,From the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.12,0:15:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.08,0:15:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The wind born on the sea
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.54,0:15:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,brings blessings by blowing on Cocoyashi Village.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.09,0:15:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just wind. The rain, clouds, rainbows...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything comes from the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.84,0:15:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Say...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.55,0:15:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,then where does the sea come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.51,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,– What?! \N– Nami.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.77,0:15:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give Bellemere-{\i1}san{\i0} such a hard time.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.31,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Nojiko...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami, you really are a curious girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami...!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you did it again!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.63,0:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The lady at the bookshop \Nstormed into the house in a rage.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.08,0:15:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go home. The dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.79,0:15:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Bellemere-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.04,0:15:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's beyond that sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.97,0:15:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what lies beyond the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you were a marine?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.72,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was, but the sea is too big.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.17,0:16:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna see... what's beyond the sea...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.56,0:16:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can go beyond that sea...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a strong child.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really want, \Nyou can go anywhere you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.53,0:16:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I've decided!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.28,0:16:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna use my navigation skills \Nto travel to all the world's oceans
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.17,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and make a world map of everything I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.16,0:16:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure will...!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. I definitely will... some day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.21,0:16:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I will complete my own world map.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.17,0:16:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.63,0:16:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoopie!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.39,0:16:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.01,0:16:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,– Amazing! Amazing! \N– Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.77,0:16:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.15,0:16:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been working hard. \NAre you done?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.61,0:16:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No... But what is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.10,0:16:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you guys doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.24,0:16:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleaning.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty fun. Wanna do it, too, Nami?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? It's noisy.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.83,0:17:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! The Smooth Skin Soap?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.70,0:17:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.21,0:17:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay! No problem!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.22,0:17:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.10,0:17:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.01,0:17:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bungee... Jump!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.31,0:17:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Move away!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.69,0:17:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.52,0:17:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.94,0:17:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! My map...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.79,0:17:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were drawing a map?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.58,0:17:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Map?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what your "work" was...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.63,0:17:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only map in the world \Nthat recorded our journey
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,after entering the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.97,0:18:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream is to complete my own world map!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.06,0:18:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.52,0:18:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami...!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If "sorry" were enough, \Nthere'd be no need for the Navy!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.78,0:18:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, leave already.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.20,0:18:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, you'll be fined 100,000 Berries!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.62,0:18:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, I think so, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.91,0:18:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I think so, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.33,0:18:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What?! You, too?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now, Luffy, cheer up.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.62,0:18:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, those guys always get in my way...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.58,0:18:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.36,0:18:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm? Smells like rain...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.79,0:19:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a problem! Luffy! Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.79,0:19:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a problem! The clouds...!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiders have ten legs.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they have eight.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.98,0:19:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that doesn't matter! Wake up!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.39,0:19:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,– Centipedes have 100 legs... \N– Usopp! Sanji!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.10,0:19:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up! Zoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.92,0:19:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.64,0:19:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a problem!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami...!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.23,0:19:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fined 100,000 Berries!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh... What should I do...?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.74,0:19:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do say so myself, this is perfect!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I a genius or what?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.08,0:19:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.13,0:19:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.96,0:19:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.97,0:19:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What were you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.47,0:20:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me before it got this bad?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.80,0:20:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... you said we'd \Nbe fined 100,000 Berries...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.89,0:20:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You dummy...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.15,0:20:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys! \NHow long are you gonna keep sleeping?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.78,0:20:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,– It's a tornado! It's a tornado! \N– It's obvious!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Zoro! Fold the sails!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.53,0:20:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.61,0:20:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Chopper! \NSecure the stuff on the deck using ropes!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.83,0:20:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.97,0:20:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Turn to starboard!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.83,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Umph!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Point the bow of the ship away from the tornado,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.34,0:20:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,or we're gonna get swallowed!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.63,0:20:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.68,0:20:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.56,0:20:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.31,0:20:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If my precious map gets washed \Naway by waves or something,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll all pay...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,dearly.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.44,0:21:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She really is scary...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The atmospheric pressure has risen \Nand the rain has stopped, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.08,0:21:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your work. You can rest now!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.04,0:21:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.04,0:21:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll go back to work, \Nso watch the clouds again.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.80,0:21:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not done yet?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.55,0:21:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.10,0:21:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My goal is to draw up the world map.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.36,0:21:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just finished the first one.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.89,0:21:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The real work starts from here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.09,0:21:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really going at it...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.18,0:21:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I like Nami-{\i1}san{\i0} that way, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.10,0:21:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there'll be a \N100,000-Berry fine again...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.28,0:21:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been reading all this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.36,0:21:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, unfurl the sails!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.86,0:21:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.62,0:21:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.08,0:21:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.90,0:21:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.61,0:23:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you know about the Navy's curry?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.12,0:23:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.95,0:23:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's famous.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.83,0:23:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that the chef on each ship \Ncompetes with all the others.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.37,0:23:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah? That sounds yummy.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.87,0:23:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The kid who fell from a Navy ship \Nearlier says he is a probationary cook.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.71,0:23:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It reminds me of my time at the sea restaurant...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.84,0:23:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.13,0:23:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A Recipe Handed Down! \NSanji, the Iron Man of Curry
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.84,0:23:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
